{
  "stem": "1354.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it started to be hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We couldn't get enough bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I remember getting up 5:00 in the morning to go to-- we were lucky, because right next to our home was a bakery.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we were going just out-- out of our door, and we stayed in the line.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So every one of us got up to be in the line to get the loaf of-- loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then it came-- pardon me?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know what to-- in the beginning, we didn't realize what-- what happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to-- I used to live there, where my school was a big space there, and they were stationed there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were there shaving and, you know, themselves, and eating, and laughing, and-- and we were looking at them like-- we were scared.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know what to-- one thing I remember when the war broke out, immediately my father send my brother quick to the bank to take out what-- whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "His head was working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whatever it was-- it was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then there start to be stories like they were catching people on the street to work and-- with the brooms on the streets, you know, to sweep out the-- the streets.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were catching those Orthodox Jews and-- and cutting off, right there on the street, the payot and-- and the-- the beards.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was a scary scary, scary thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And well, right away there was shortage of food and shortage of everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was kind-- but it wasn't so bad, because we were still together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then came a time they say everybody has to go to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my parents were afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They didn't want to go to ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we went outskirts to Kocmyrzow.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
